creator: WhatStyle Limited
descriptionHtml:
The official Wishface app. Download to make appointments and turn on notifications to get all of our latest updates. Wishface provides aesthetics and beauty with the highest quality products used from our beautiful salon based in Newcastle-Upon-Tyne. We are also a CPD certified member offering aesthetics training.

Key features include:⁣
- Book with us directly⁣
- Manage your own appointments ⁣
- Join our waitlist⁣
- Receive all of our latest notifications⁣
- View staff and service details⁣
- Browse products⁣
- View all of our latest gallery posts⁣
⁣
Welcome to Wishface! Download the app today.
descriptionShort: Keep up to date with all the latest from Wishface.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This is the initial release of the Wishface app.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Reschedule your existing bookings.
- Remove services from the cart while booking
- Improved email verification and forgot-password functionality
- Ability to update the email address on your account (you will be required to reauthenticate if you decide to do this)
- Find us using Apple Maps, Google Maps and Citymapper. Even better, arrange trips to us with the Uber and Lyft apps
- Plus some great behind the scenes bug-fixes and optimisation improvements

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This update is one of our smaller updates which includes:

- The ability for us to require at least one payment card be on file while booking
- A resolution to an error which frequently occurred during the booking rescheduling process
- A bug which in some cases caused the location on Google Maps to be shown incorrectly
